Apache 1.3.27 or higher

PHP 4.3.3 or higher
	 - with-gd
	 - enable-memory-limit
	 - enable-sockets (Squiz Server only)
	 - enable-pcntl (Squiz Server only)
	 
PEAR - Base = 1.3
     - Mime_Mail = 1.2.1
     - Archive_Tar = 1.1
	 - XML_HTMLSax = 2.1.2 (spell checker)
	 - XML_Parser = 1.0.1
     - DB = 1.6.2

HTML Tidy : http://tidy.sourceforge.net/

Databases : 
 - PostgreSQL 7.4 or higher

GD : 2.0.1 or higher
